Package: numerals
Title: UTF Numeral Systems
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Joe",
           family = "Roe",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "joe@joeroe.io",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1011-1244"))
Description: Extends the base numeric types so that they can be formatted and
   printed as UTF characters in international numeral systems. Currently 
   supports Eastern Arabic ('ar') and Persian ('fa') numerals.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Suggests: 
    testthat
Encoding: UTF-8
